So, here's some kerbal organizations I make(you can make too!)

SCP foundation (SCP-KB): 

After thousands of useless attempts, the SCP foundation on Earth had finally made a teleportation device. The first test crew made their way to Kerbin, and they build Site-KB-1 on the grasslands. Now, they had contained many anomalies, such as deep space kraken(SCP-KB-002) and the strut(SCP-KB-005).

Kerbal Atomic Union: 

This organization controls every Uranium Mine and every nuclear power plant on Kerbin.  They sell energy from the nuclear power plant in a cheap prize.
